article_title: Obamacare Brings Wellpoint Even Bigger Profits Than Expected

article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen

og.description: Wellpoint (WLP), one of the nation’s largest health insurers, joined the parade of health plans increasing its enrollment of new privately insured members and Medicaid enrollees this year thanks to the Affordable Care Act, raising its financial guidance for the fourth time this year. Speaking on the company’s third-quarter earnings call [...]
